Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇者之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.19,0:01:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去成為真正的救世主的身邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛到傳說的救世主身邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.94,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一話\N救世主是小學四年級生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,起身了,又要遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起床啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡 我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要穿滾軸鞋上學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快遲到的話就要穿這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個穿過龍神池便到學校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是聰明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.39,0:04:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神池內住了條很可怕的龍會把壞孩子吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.01,0:04:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的事一點也不可怕\N我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.09,0:04:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,這樣的東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神大人,我明天會早起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會和媽媽鬥嘴,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也會穿上鞋上學\N還有…不會吃剩蘿葡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上壘!上壘!出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.15,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己覺得有型的東西\N可愛的東西,什麼都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.30,0:05:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美,你要做什麼?\N我家的芝羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你家的貓嗎?很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡你要做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機械人…我要造機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機械人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美 我也要做機械人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞瞬也是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼要跟我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才不要跟我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我先說要造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒什麼關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.41,0:06:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊,那來比\N誰的機械人造得有型吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊,不過對你來說\N也是多此一舉罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.11,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好有型 真厲害呢\N瞬果然很厲害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.09,0:06:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以碰的,好了\N你們借開吧,由美,請看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很棒呢,你真厲害,瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.52,0:07:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡我真是太高興了\N渡,你也快給我們看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.99,0:07:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想看我的嗎?瞬\N那你便看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的比試是我勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.55,0:07:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?\N那也算是機械人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機械人是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這樣奇怪嗎?\N雖然和我想像的有點出入…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉?這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確把這個放在龍神池的祠上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛 你覺得是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏?哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看清楚的話這個也是很有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美\N我和瞬的機械人哪個較有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡勝出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.39,0:08:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神池的龍,我已不怕你了\N因為我有很強的幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出來的話便出來看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不替你取個名字不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫什麼好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.76,0:08:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍…神…丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定了\N你的名字便是龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,起床了,起床啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字是… 戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看見龍了吧?\N看…看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.27,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婆婆,這孩子便是傳說中的救世主嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說他可以\N令創界山的七色彩虹甦醒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他會把這條麾沙村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從古怪的天氣的侵襲中解放出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.91,0:11:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令村園裏再一次充滿一片翠綠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相傳每當創界山有危機時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.94,0:11:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拯救它的人便會從天而降\N他的名字便是渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會與龍神一起把邪惡打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個救世主現在在這裏出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.66,0:11:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是救世主?\N救世主是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起學校的風紀更偉大嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要拯救這個世界的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位\N把救世主大人帶往神祠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幹什麼?我要回家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?很像龍神池呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…沒有水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為創界山的彩虹失去了色彩的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神池的水也干了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是到了未來\N或是過去的世界了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!說起來這種事\N我好像在哪裏聽過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.96,0:12:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是時間停止…不\N時間加速…不是,時間故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在亂說什麼?跟我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?石浮在空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是創界山的碎片\N渡,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們麾沙村\N代代相傳的戰士的裝束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你穿上它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以穿嗎?我一直很想要那樣的滾軸鞋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾軸鞋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出場姿勢已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,那座便是創界山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.06,0:13:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩!很巨大的山呢,奇怪了\N有一條沒有顏色的彩虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.00,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從來沒有人見過他的真面目的\N邪惡大王多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但支配了和平的創界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.29,0:13:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還令七色彩虹變成了白色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此這條麾沙村\N也變得異常起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.27,0:13:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我是要登上創界山\N和多惡達作戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像做夢一樣的事呢\N不過沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來干\N不幫助有困難的人不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是一段很艱苦的旅程啊\N你有心理準備了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救護車也會害怕的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是救護車,是救世主啊\N你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.31,0:14:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是問你名字\N你竟然取笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.54,0:14:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?你不可向忍部一族\N第13代首領出手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首…首領?他說首領…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子是忍部一族的頭目啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭目?你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,我是頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.08,0:14:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彩虹啊\N有彩虹從創界山那邊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.92,0:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人來了 有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害的傢伙終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.14,0:14:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麾沙村的人聽著\N我是創界山偉大的支配者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.91,0:14:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達大人的七人眾的\N其中一人,第一界層的波士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.67,0:15:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古路治大人的左右手\N舒華新力加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很長的自我介紹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.49,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了得到了創界山\N附近的村落也要全部支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.45,0:15:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是多惡達大人的命令\N不聽命令的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便會有可怕的遭遇\N你們立即發誓效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.05,0:15:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?真是傲慢的小孩\N你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.43,0:15:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救護車,渡\N救護車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是救世主,不是救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?我是救世主,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫救世主真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話,讓這部戰鬥\N猩猩的一擊令你們清醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.95,0:15:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,這裏交給渡\N我們回村吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我終於來了,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.43,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,用劍啊\N使用勇者之劍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇者之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.09,0:16:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔出來了 好!來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子一點也不強呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.97,0:16:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題嗎?\N因為是傳說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.96,0:16:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真卑鄙,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜歡卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,怎樣啊?救世主\N火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.49,0:16:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法 火炎之術,小心火警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了說,那萬能鞋\N拍一下的話便會有輪出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在拍一次便會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事應該早說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我給你送命的一發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,沒子彈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.95,0:17:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!小子,你在那裏不要動\N絕對不要動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是這樣上彈\N戰鬥猩猩便是無敵的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎辦好?\N怎樣和那巨大的傢伙戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.90,0:17:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是龍神丸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.70,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,把勇者之劍\N向著天空呼叫我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…龍神丸在和我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點,渡\N我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.73,0:18:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個便是傳說中的龍神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?\N那傢伙…這不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.80,0:19:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是龍啊\N又到了一個奇怪的世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧,渡,這裏是龍神丸\N也就是我的體內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,抓住龍的雙角吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,現在起我和你一起戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.84,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會照你的意思行動\N便可以戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我什麼也看不見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去吧,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不抓緊的話會掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為可以勝過我\N舒華新力加的力量嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸有無敵的正義力量\N不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓下去,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.59,0:20:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話便用炮收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,用劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.11,0:20:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很厲害啊,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像已經知道了\N登龍劍的使用方法了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸的劍是叫登龍劍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他來了,渡!\N死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又沒彈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我記著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要向多惡達大人\N報告這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.02,0:21:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你要和龍神丸一起\N拯救創界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.40,0:21:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從多惡達的魔爪中救出眾神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會把彩虹\N恢復七色給你看,等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.86,0:21:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先到第一界層的東方\N多高山上的雙龍巖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那處有顆\N擁有不可思議力量的珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.59,0:21:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那得到手的話\N一定可以幫助你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.00,0:21:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了,多高山的雙龍巖\N去吧,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.37,0:22:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊

